function normalizeOcrText(text=''){return String(text).replace(/\r/g,'').replace(/[−–—]/g,'-').replace(/[₩￦]/g,'').replace(/\u00a0/g,' ').replace(/[ \t]+/g,' ').trim()}
function repairKoreanOcr(text=''){let v=normalizeOcrText(text);const rules=[[/얼\s*음\s*왕\s*국/gi,'얼음왕국'],[/배\s*달\s*의\s*민\s*족/gi,'배달의민족'],[/내\s*계\s*좌\s*이\s*체/gi,'내 계좌 이체'],[/토\s*스\s*뱅\s*크/gi,'토스뱅크'],[/(?:《|<|K|X)?\s*8\s*국\s*민/gi,'KB국민'],[/1\s*8\s*기\s*업/gi,'IBK기업'],[/나\s*라\s*사\s*랑\s*체\s*크\s*카\s*드/gi,'나라사랑체크카드'],[/카\s*드\s*캐\s*시\s*백/gi,'카드 캐시백'],[/삼\s*성\s*서\s*울\s*정\s*형\s*외\s*과\s*의\s*원/gi,'삼성서울정형외과의원'],[/R\s*E\s*N\s*D\s*E\s*R\s*\.\s*C\s*O\s*M/gi,'RENDER.COM'],[/G\s*S\s*2\s*5/gi,'GS25'],[/세\s*븐\s*일\s*레\s*븐/gi,'세븐일레븐'],[/쿠\s*팡/gi,'쿠팡'],[/S\s*t\s*e\s*a\s*m/gi,'Steam']];for(const [re,to] of rules)v=v.replace(re,to);return v.replace(/\s{2,}/g,' ').trim()}
function categoryForMemo(memo,type='expense'){const v=repairKoreanOcr(memo);if(type==='income'&&/캐시백|환급/i.test(v))return'환급';const rules=[['대출',/대출이자|원리금/i],['카드값',/현대카드|카드대금|카드값|결제예정금액/i],['이체',/내 계좌 이체|계좌 이체|송금|카카오페이 충전|→/i],['카페',/스타벅스|메가커피|컴포즈|투썸|이디야|카페|커피|빽다방/i],['식비',/배달의민족|배민|얼음왕국|버거|피자|치킨|음식|식당|배달|쿠팡이츠|요기요/i],['의료',/병원|의원|약국|치과|한의원|외과|내과/i],['교통',/피플카|택시|카카오.?T|주유|주차|하이패스|버스|지하철/i],['취미',/Steam|스팀|게임|넷플릭스|PlayStation|Xbox/i],['쇼핑',/쿠팡|네이버페이|무신사|쇼핑|퍼퓸|바디워시/i],['생활',/GS25|세븐일레븐|CU\b|편의점|다이소|마트/i],['고정비',/통신|보험|전기|가스|수도|월세|관리비|구독|render\.com|onrender/i]];for(const [c,re]of rules)if(re.test(v))return c;return'기타'}
function accountForMemo(memo){const v=repairKoreanOcr(memo);if(/체크카드|신용카드|나라사랑|현대카드|카드 캐시백|해외결제|카드$/i.test(v))return'카드';if(/내 계좌 이체|계좌|은행|토스뱅크|KB국민|IBK기업|카카오뱅크|통장 이자|대출이자|카카오페이 충전/i.test(v))return'은행';return'은행'}
function makeDate(year,month,day){const d=new Date(year,month-1,day);if(d.getFullYear()!==year||d.getMonth()!==month-1||d.getDate()!==day)return'';return`${year}-${String(month).padStart(2,'0')}-${String(day).padStart(2,'0')}`}
function parseAmountLine(line=''){const clean=normalizeOcrText(line);if(/USD\s*[\d,.]+/i.test(clean)&&!/[+-]?\s*\d[\d,]{2,}\s*원/.test(clean))return null;const matches=[...clean.matchAll(/([+-]?)\s*(\d[\d,]{2,})\s*원?/g)];if(!matches.length)return null;const krw=matches.filter(m=>Number(m[2].replaceAll(',',''))>=100);if(!krw.length)return null;const chosen=krw[krw.length-1];const amount=Number(chosen[2].replaceAll(',',''));if(!amount)return null;return{amount,type:chosen[1]==='+'?'income':'expense',confidence:krw.length>1?.91:.97,adjusted:krw.length>1,raw:clean}}
function dayHeader(line=''){const m=normalizeOcrText(line).match(/^(\d{1,2})\s*일(?:\s*[월화수목금토일]요일)?$/);return m?Number(m[1]):null}
function looksNoise(line=''){const v=normalizeOcrText(line);return!v||/^(검색|전체|일|월|화|수|목|금|토|할부|내역 더보기|지난 3개월)$/i.test(v)||/^\d{1,2}:\d{2}$/.test(v)||/^\d{1,2}\s*월$/.test(v)||/^[+-]?\d[\d,]*원?$/.test(v)}
function sameParsedTransaction(a,b){return String(a.tx_date)===String(b.tx_date)&&String(a.tx_type)===String(b.tx_type)&&Number(a.amount)===Number(b.amount)&&repairKoreanOcr(a.memo||'').toLowerCase()===repairKoreanOcr(b.memo||'').toLowerCase()}
function parseFinanceOcrPages(pageTexts,year,month,pageHints=[]){let carryDay=null,overlap=0,cancelled=0;const all=[];pageTexts.forEach((pageText,pageIndex)=>{const lines=normalizeOcrText(pageText).split('\n').map(repairKoreanOcr).filter(Boolean);let currentDay=carryDay||Number(pageHints[pageIndex])||null,pending=null,seenHeader=false;function finish(){if(!pending)return;const memo=repairKoreanOcr(pending.memo.join(' ').trim())||'사진 거래';if(/취소|승인취소|결제 취소/i.test(memo)){cancelled++;pending=null;return}const date=currentDay?makeDate(year,month,currentDay):'';const tx={localId:`ocr-${pageIndex}-${all.length}`,tx_date:date,tx_type:pending.amount.type,account:accountForMemo(memo),category:categoryForMemo(memo,pending.amount.type),amount:pending.amount.amount,memo,confidence:Math.min(pending.amount.confidence,date?.92:.38,memo==='사진 거래'?.35:.9),uncertain:!date||memo==='사진 거래'||pending.amount.confidence<.75,include:true,saved:false,sourceIndex:pageIndex,reasons:[pending.amount.adjusted?'복수 원화 금액 중 마지막 금액 사용':'원화 금액 인식',date?'날짜 그룹 연결':'날짜 불확실']};const duplicate=all.some(row=>sameParsedTransaction(row,tx));if(duplicate)overlap++;else all.push(tx);pending=null}
  for(const raw of lines){const header=dayHeader(raw);if(header){finish();currentDay=header;carryDay=header;seenHeader=true;continue}const amount=parseAmountLine(raw);if(amount){finish();if(/취소|승인취소|결제 취소/i.test(raw)){cancelled++;pending=null;continue}pending={amount,memo:[]};continue}if(pending&&!looksNoise(raw)&&!/^USD\b/i.test(raw))pending.memo.push(raw)}finish();if(seenHeader)carryDay=currentDay});return{transactions:all,stats:{overlap,cancelled}}}
function sectionBeforeHistory(text=''){const normalized=normalizeOcrText(text);const index=normalized.search(/신체\s*변화|신체변화/);return index>=0?normalized.slice(0,index):normalized}
function historySection(text=''){const normalized=normalizeOcrText(text);const index=normalized.search(/신체\s*변화|신체변화/);return index>=0?normalized.slice(index):''}
function firstNumberAfter(text,labelPattern){const re=new RegExp(`${labelPattern}[^\\d+\\-]{0,35}([+\\-]?\\d+(?:\\.\\d+)?)`,'i');const m=text.match(re);return m?Number(m[1]):null}
function parseInbody650Text(text=''){const current=sectionBeforeHistory(text),history=historySection(text);const dateMatch=current.match(/검사일시?[^\d]*(20\d{2})[.\/-](\d{1,2})[.\/-](\d{1,2})(?:\s+(\d{1,2}:\d{2}))?/i)||current.match(/(20\d{2})[.\/-](\d{1,2})[.\/-](\d{1,2})\s+(\d{1,2}:\d{2})/);const date=dateMatch?`${dateMatch[1]}-${String(dateMatch[2]).padStart(2,'0')}-${String(dateMatch[3]).padStart(2,'0')}`:'';const get=label=>firstNumberAfter(current,label);const segmental={};for(const [key,label]of [['rightArm','오른팔'],['leftArm','왼팔'],['trunk','몸통'],['rightLeg','오른다리'],['leftLeg','왼다리']]){const re=new RegExp(`${label}[^\\d]{0,18}(\\d+(?:\\.\\d+)?)\\s*(?:kg)?[^\\d]{0,18}(\\d+(?:\\.\\d+)?)\\s*%`,'i'),m=current.match(re);if(m)segmental[key]={kg:Number(m[1]),pct:Number(m[2])}}
 const result={date,time:dateMatch?.[4]||'',weight:get('체중(?=\\s|:)'),smm:get('골격근량'),fatMass:get('체지방량'),bmi:get('BMI'),bodyFatPercent:get('체지방률'),score:get('(?:InBody\\s*Score|인바디점수)'),phaseAngle:get('(?:전신\\s*)?위상각'),smi:get('SMI'),targetWeight:get('적정체중'),weightControl:get('체중조절'),fatControl:get('지방조절'),muscleControl:get('근육조절'),ecwRatio:get('세포외수분비'),icw:get('세포내수분'),ecw:get('세포외수분(?!비)'),bmr:get('기초대사량'),whr:get('복부지방률'),visceralFat:get('내장지방레벨'),obesityDegree:get('비만도'),boneMineral:get('골무기질량'),bodyCellMass:get('체세포량'),segmental,history:{dates:[],weight:[],smm:[],fatMass:[],bodyFatPercent:[],ecwRatio:[]},uncertain:[]};
 const dates=[...history.matchAll(/20\d{2}[.\/-]\d{1,2}[.\/-]\d{1,2}/g)].map(m=>m[0].replaceAll('.','-').replaceAll('/','-')).slice(0,8);result.history.dates=dates;function series(labelPattern,key){const m=history.match(new RegExp(`${labelPattern}[^\\n]*\\n?([\\s\\S]{0,180})`,'i'));if(!m)return;const vals=[...m[1].matchAll(/(?:^|\s)(\d+(?:\.\d+)?)(?=\s|$)/g)].map(x=>Number(x[1])).slice(0,dates.length);result.history[key]=vals}series('체중','weight');series('골격근량','smm');series('체지방량','fatMass');series('체지방률','bodyFatPercent');series('세포외수분비','ecwRatio');for(const key of ['date','weight','smm','fatMass','bmi','bodyFatPercent'])if(result[key]===null||result[key]==='')result.uncertain.push(key);return result}
